## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- [Bundler](https://bundler.io/) v4.0
- PostgreSQL 18
- Redis 8.6
- Ruby 3.4.7
- Typesense Server 30.1

### Set Up Font Awesome

Navigate to [Get Started with Font Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/start) to sign up and add a new icon kit. Create an app configuration using the included `config/application.yml.example` file, then plug in your new kit:

```bash
cd /path/to/your/repo
cp config/application.yml.example config/application.yml
```

Open `config/application.yml` and replace `font_awesome_kit_url` with your kit's url.

### Build and Run

```bash
cd /path/to/your/repo

# Set up everything + start the development server
bin/setup

# Set up everything + don't start the development server
bin/setup --skip-server

# Reset back to factory settings
bin/setup --reset
```

Open [localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) in your web browser.

